### **Advantages over competitors:**
- **ğŸš€ Multi-Hardware Support** - CPU, GPU, Intel Loihi, SpiNNaker
- **âš¡ Ultra-Low Power** - 1000x less energy than traditional NNs
- **ğŸ§¬ Bio-Inspired Learning** - STDP, Homeostasis, Metaplasticity
